title: Living In Total Victory | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Living In Total Victory | Joel Osteen
description:
God paid the price so we can live in total victory. It's time to take hold of His promises in every area of your life. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
